OL,3,CEE warns Christmas shoppers over
OL,4,Crising threat of scams
OL,6,FThe mobile operator is warning that
OL,7,Fthe additional urgency that can often
OL,8,Farise when shopping in the run-up to
OL,9,FChristmas is something scammers are
OL,10,Fkeen to prey on, and in response has
OL,11,Fhighlighted a number of scam tactics,
OL,12,Fincluding those which use time
OL,13,Fpressure or impersonation in an
OL,14,Fattempt to get money or personal
OL,15,Finformation out of consumers.
