OL,3,CEE warns Christmas shoppers over
OL,4,Crising threat of scams
OL,6,FThe firm is urging consumers to focus
OL,7,Fon a number of factors in order to
OL,8,Fprotect themselves: creating strong
OL,9,Fpasswords, being vigilant to random
OL,10,Fcalls from unknown numbers,
OL,11,Fconsidering using encryption-based
OL,12,Fproducts, being suspicious of web
OL,13,Flinks from unknown sources, checking
OL,14,Fall devices to ensure they have the
OL,15,Fmost recent security updates
OL,16,Finstalled, not sharing personal
OL,17,Finformation unnecessarily and trusting
OL,18,Ftheir instincts.
