OL,3,CEE warns Christmas shoppers over
OL,4,Crising threat of scams
OL,6,FRichard Wainer, regulatory affairs
OL,7,Fdirector at BT Group, of which EE is a
OL,8,Fpart, said: "Our commitment to
OL,9,Fprotecting our customers against scams
OL,10,Fis unwavering.
OL,12,F"The festive season is the time of
OL,13,Fyear consumers are most likely to be
OL,14,Fscammed and it's even more important
OL,15,Fthat people have the tools they need
OL,16,Fto guard against attempted scams.
