OL,3,CEE warns Christmas shoppers over
OL,4,Crising threat of scams
OL,6,F"We know people are increasingly
OL,7,Fanxious that they or their loved ones
OL,8,Fwill be targeted by scammers in the
OL,9,Flead-up to Christmas, but by raising
OL,10,Fawareness of some of the most common
OL,11,Ftechniques and providing advice and
OL,12,Fservices such as Scam Guard, we are
OL,13,Fdetermined to continue to protect
OL,14,Fconsumers against fraudsters."
