OL,3,CEE warns Christmas shoppers over
OL,4,Crising threat of scams
OL,6,FA new study by EE found that one in
OL,7,Ffour UK shoppers have either been
OL,8,Ftargeted or fallen victim to scammers
OL,9,Fduring the festive period, with EE's
OL,10,Fsecurity partners Norton estimating
OL,11,Fscam victims lose on average around
OL,12,F#1,000 each.
